Libera WFOV Camera Instrument properties
========================================================================

   This instrument kernel (I-kernel) contains references to the mounting
   alignment, internal and FOV geometry for the Libera Camera.
 
Version and Date
----------------------------------------------------------

   The TEXT_KERNEL_ID stores version information of loaded project text
   kernels. Each entry associated with the keyword is a string that consists
   of four parts: the kernel name, version, entry date, and type. For example,
   the JPSS I-kernel might have an entry as follows:
 
           TEXT_KERNEL_ID += 'LIBERA CAM V0.0 13-OCTOBER-2022 IK'
