Platform ID
----------------------------------------------------------
 
   The WFOV camera instrument is mounted on the Libera Azimuth platform, which is
   connected to the JPSS Spacecraft body. Therefore the value in the keywords below 
   is -143013000.
 
           \begindata
 
           INS-143013010_PLATFORM_ID = ( -143013000 )
 
